comment: If as a conseqence of the occurence of the circumstance ` ph ` , when the obstacle ` ps ` is removed, ` ch ` takes place, then from the circumstance that ` ch ` does not take place while ` ph ` occurs the occurence of the obstacle ` ps ` can be inferred.
